('Mads D Danesoe', 'Mads D', 'Danesoe', 'Transforming Hospitality Through Storytelling & Systems | General Manager, Kamala Beach Estate | AI-Driven Cultural Projects in Phuket', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/mads-d-danesoe-b55472259', 'mads-d-danesoe-b55472259', $${"about": "I believe every place has a story — it just needs to be told well.\n\nAt Kamala Beach Estate, I lead one of Phuket’s most quietly beautiful properties, where we’re reimagining what hospitality can be. Not through slogans, but through storytelling: from the creation of a Thai Medicinal Botanical Garden to dining experiences that connect Thai food, wine, and culture.\n\nMy background spans 35 years in leadership — including two decades in IT and digital systems — now applied to designing smarter, more human hotels. I use AI, structure, and narrative to shape projects that guests remember and teams take pride in.\n\nOutside of work, I explore Thailand the same way I manage: with curiosity, precision, and consistency.\n\nAs a Level 10 Google Local Guide, I’ve visited and documented hundreds of locations across the country — more than 1,000 reviews and 25,000 photos, viewed over 150 million times.\n\nFor me, it’s not tourism; it’s cultural mapping — a way of understanding how people and places connect.\n\nI also collaborate with Window on Phuket on storytelling initiatives and contribute to Skål International Phuket, where I help connect professionals through shared experiences and authentic exchange.\n\nMy focus sits at the intersection of technology, culture, and hospitality — proving that when systems and storytelling align, even a hotel can become a story worth following.\n\nFocus areas: Strategic hospitality leadership · AI integration · Cultural storytelling · Digital transformation · Tourism community building", "addressCountryOnly": "Thailand", "addressWithCountry": "Phuket, Thailand", "addressWithoutCountry": "Phuket", "backgroundPic": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D16AQHUHONYYEigaw/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/0/1722906808924?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=WUGsLFfF9YjgeOgHectC2VvZ0oRyapf6CCGu99XVdYg", "companyLinkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/kamala-beach-estate/", "companyName": "Kamala Beach Estate", "connections": "210", "creatorWebsite/0/category": "PERSONAL", "creatorWebsite/0/url": "KamalaBeachEstate.com", "currentJobDuration": "3 yrs 1 mo", "currentJobDurationInYrs": "3.08", "experiences/0/companyId": "43215037", "experiences/0/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/kamala-beach-estate/", "experiences/0/companyName": "Kamala Beach Estate", "experiences/0/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:43215037", "experiences/0/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/0/jobDescription": "Lead the daily operations and long-term development of a boutique beachfront property on Phuket’s west coast.\nApply decades of management and IT experience to create structured, transparent systems for hospitality, maintenance, and communication.\nCurrent focus areas include developing a Thai Medicinal Botanical Garden, refining guest experience through AI-supported operations, and using storytelling to connect the property’s natural setting with its cultural roots.\nBring an explorer’s eye and storyteller’s discipline to every part of the estate — turning place, process, and people into one coherent narrative.\nCollaborate with Window on Phuket and Skål International Phuket to strengthen Phuket’s professional and creative network.", "experiences/0/jobLocation": "Kamala, Phuket, Thailand", "experiences/0/jobStartedOn": "4-2023", "experiences/0/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/0/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C560BAQGt9jy0jNTroA/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1630603154720?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=FcpofU2rzdxuhrfLHd2SHnVyg3imzo_269luTC7tYdQ", "experiences/0/title": "General Manager", "experiences/1/companyId": "69618470", "experiences/1/companyLink1": "https://