s its reputation as one of the best nightlife destinations in the region.", "experiences/0/jobLocation": "Bangkok, Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/0/jobStartedOn": "5-2023", "experiences/0/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/0/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQFQohU5M56pQQ/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1631343480200?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=zat3QvdPtRQBPFK9y3ZP65sV10lyo-uaPuU0J5_gkTs", "experiences/0/title": "General Manager", "experiences/1/companyId": "18383601", "experiences/1/companyIndustry": "Business Consulting and Services", "experiences/1/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/stark-networks-pfo/", "experiences/1/companyName": "Stark Networks HK", "experiences/1/companySize": "2-10", "experiences/1/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:18383601", "experiences/1/companyWebsite": "http://www.starknetworks.ch", "experiences/1/employmentType": "Contract", "experiences/1/jobDescription": "Stark Networks is a single-family office operating on a private-client, private-project basis. We represent and support associates, clients, and partners across a carefully selected portfolio. The firm primarily focuses on projects in Asia, particularly in the areas of film production and project-based investment.\n\nOur commitments span a curated slate of ventures, with a strong emphasis on private equity and high-value opportunities that require strategic capital to close. My role involves supporting relationship management, cross-border communications, and European liaison efforts tied to these investments and developments.", "experiences/1/jobLocation": "Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/1/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "11-2020", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "true", "experiences/1/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D560BAQHRjXIa_74Egg/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1703997431826/stark_networks_pfo_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=12VUOAgdQ58pxbwf1v9rAjShHTZm7R1IsuDsMduXydI", "expe